      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FASHION ICON (8) raced three wide without cover from this barrier and stuck on for fourth two back then was well fancied last week but bombed the start. Capable and owns a good record at this circuit and distance so only needs to get things right to go close. ALLSTARZZZ FRANKIE (6) made good improvement second up when he led and showed plenty of fight to score last week at this circuit and distance, getting home by a head. Up in grade but should be fitter again so he is capable of getting the job done. FLYING COLOURS NZ (3) has been racing at Menangle of late, finishing runner-up two back. Came from this barrier to win at Blayney the last time he raced outside of the city. JORGE STREET (4) worked last start but draws better and was only 4.4m away at Menangle prior.",
